The '''Guatemalan National Natural History Museum''' or '''Museo de Historia Natural''' is a [[national museum|national]] [[natural history museum]] in [[Guatemala City]], [[Guatemala]]. The museum has an extensive collection of Guatemalan flora and fauna specimens, and has a significant number of archives from geology and paleontology in the country.

