est represented Triassic theropod from Europe and one of the largest known. |- | * ''[[Plateosaurus]]'' | 214-204 Ma, Carnian to Norian | Trossingen Formation, [[Bavaria]], Germany | |- | * ''[[Thecodontosaurus]]'' | Norian to Rhaetian | | |- |}
